## 耳 Color Variant Schema (`colors` / `Colors`)

Represents customized dyed variants of the item.

### TypeScript Definition:
```typescript
interface Color {
  name: string;      // Swatch option name (e.g. "L盻ｭa xanh")
  hex: string;       // 6-digit hex code for circular swatch rendering (e.g. "#84A9C0")
  imageUrl?: string; // Optional variant specific image path that hot-swaps on click
}
```

### C# DTO Definition:
```csharp
public class ColorDto
{
    public string Name { get; set; } = null!;
    public string Hex { get; set; } = null!;
    public string? ImageUrl { get; set; }
}
```

